   "source": [
    "Recall the definition of an eigenvector $v$ with eigenvalue $\\lambda$ for some matrix $A$:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$ A v = \\lambda v $$\n",
    "\n",
    "In our case, $\\lambda = 1$, and $v = p_*$."
